snippet.title: Arcane Quest HD Remaster Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Arcane Quest HD Remaster is the remake of the original Arcane Quest mobile game, the first chapter of the series.
Arcane Quest is a mobile RPG game with board game style inspired by the classics such as HeroQuest and Dungeons & Dragons. 

The game is available for free on Android, iOS and Windows 10. 

More info at: arcane-quest.com
